gorr

GOR-R: R library for remote execution of GOR queries and authorization with WuXi NextCode gateway API.

gorr__check_error()

Check if response contains an error (not http error) from the direct query service

Custom wrapper for stop() with formated error messages

Get query status from api. This is not a public function, but is called from gor_query

gorr__post_query()

Post query to api. This is not a public function, but is called from gor_query

gorr__reconnect()
